			<node ID="ID_771774525" TEXT="Network on Chip vs System on Chip- Which one is better? Network on chip (NOC) and System on chip (SOC) both are sub system based integrated circuit that integrates even component of a particular system. But just as the name suggests NOC is designed for an organized network but SOC is meant for an organized device like computer. This why NO" />
