		<node ID="ID_868641057" LINK="https://roseindia.net/answers/viewqa/bigdata/32988-What-are-characteristics-of-IoT-.html" TEXT="What are characteristics of IoT?">
			<node ID="ID_389464463" TEXT="Here I will discuss the features and characteristics of Internet of Things for you. Internet of Things or IoT for short is latest technologies for connected devices using Internet. IoT makes devices intelligent and communicate among them; these devices are controlled by central server for better optimization of the overall system." />
			</node>
