			<node ID="ID_1723497990" TEXT="The Internet of Things (IoT) extends from a single constrained device to a whole range of cloud systems all connected by a set of IoT protocols that allow devices and servers to talk to one another. Let&#8217;s take a look at a few IoT protocols. The next era of computing is the Internet of Things (IoT) also known as the Internet of Objects." />
			</node>
