			<node ID="ID_345669977" TEXT="The IoT grew to a completely &#8220;different Internet&#8221; so that not all existing protocols were able to satisfy its needs and provide seamless connectivity. That&#8217;s why it became a vital necessity to create specialized IoT communication protocols and standards. However some existing technologies (e.g. HTTP) are also used by the Internet of Things." />
			</node>
