		<node ID="ID_753778922" LINK="https://opensource.com/article/18/8/django-framework" TEXT="An introduction to the Django Python web app framework ">
			<node ID="ID_1800448397" TEXT="Django styles itself as a high-level Python web framework that encourages rapid development and clean pragmatic design. Built by experienced developers it takes care of much of the hassle of web development so you can focus on writing your app without needing to reinvent the wheel. And they really mean it! This massive web framework comes " />
